requestBody.description: A request to obtain more information about dedicated IP pools.

NextToken.description: A token returned from a previous call to GetDedicatedIps to indicate the position of the dedicated IP pool in the list of IP pools.

PageSize.description: The number of results to show in a single call to GetDedicatedIpsRequest. If the number of results is larger than the number you specified in this parameter, then the response includes a NextToken element, which you can use to obtain additional results.

PoolName.description: The name of the IP pool that the dedicated IP address is associated with.
